(43, 6, 3, 40, 15, 29, 29, NULL, 'Jesus Sitting on a Mountain', 'Both passages emphasize Jesus going up into a mountain and sitting down. This parallel highlights a consistent setting in Jesus'' ministry where he teaches or interacts with his disciples.', 'parallel', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
